    "title": "Junior Instructional Designer at Delhi University Digital Technologies",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Delhi University Digital Technologies. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Instructional Designer to strengthen our Jodhpur-based team.\n\nAbout Delhi University Digital Technologies:\nDelhi University Digital Technologies is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor student progress and provide timely feedback\n• Conduct doubt-clearing sessions and remedial classes for weak students\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Participate in school events, workshops, and training programs\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Contribute to school newsletter, blogs, and other publications\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Curriculum Development\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Mentoring\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Research Skills\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Referral bonus program\n• Flexible working hours\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Jodhpur, Rajasthan, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Delhi University Digital Technologies!",
